## Description {#details}

A class that represents an address range.

The range is specified using a start and an end address: &#91;Start, End).

Definition at line 22 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/addressranges-h">AddressRanges.h</a>.
